 ons close 21 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Horizon Institute for Public Serv
 ice\nLocation: Remote\nAward: Up to $100\,000 in career-development fundin
 g per participant (for unpaid or underpaid placements\, courses\, conferen
 ces\, relocation and other career costs)\, plus 1-on-1 mentorship\, dedica
 ted training\, application coaching\, hiring-manager introductions and exc
 lusive job listings. No application fee.\nDuration: 9-month part-time prog
 ramme (typically under 2 hrs/week outside an optional 4-6 week training pe
 riod)\n\nMore: https://horizonpublicservice.org/applications-open-for-hori
 zons-ai-policy-career-accelerator/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&u
