 ugh a university\, with 10% research budget and standard fringe benefits)\
 , or $80\,000–$150\,000/year (direct stipend\, with suggested 5–10% al
 location for research and travel). Compute resources available for machine
  learning research. Invitation and funding to attend the annual Center for
  Mind\, Ethics\, and Policy Summit at NYU. ELIGIBILITY: must have or be ex
 pected to receive a doctoral degree in computer science\, neuroscience\, a
